operties sufficient to allay minor irrita 1 tions remove redness and roughness prevent pore clogging soften and soothe sensative con ditions and promote skin and scalp health gen rally Such a soap combined with the purest of saponaceous ingredients and most fragrant and refreshing of flower odors is Cuticura Soap It costs but a little more it wears to a wafer and gives comfort and satisfaction every moment of its use in the toilet bath and nur sery No other soap has done so much for poor complexions red rough hands and dry thin and falling hair It has done even more for akintortured and disfigured infants children and adults when assisted by Cuticura Oint ment As a toilet soap for preserving and pur ifying the complexion hands and hair and as a skin soap for dissipating irritating and un sightly conditions of the skin Cuticura Soa has no rivals worth mentioning Its sale is greater than the worlds product of other skin soaps oombined It is sold wherever civiliza tion has penetrated It has depots in all world centers For the thirtytwo page Cuticura Booklet a"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2022-09-26T05:33:26.094Z", "group": ["ndnp/au", "university-of-alabama-tuscaloosa-al-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn85038485/1910-07-31/ed-1/?sp=3", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:au:batch_au_gaston_ver01:data:sn85038485:00340583954:1910073101:0448/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=438&w=306", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:au:batch_au_gaston_ver01:data:sn85038485:00340583954:1910073101:0448/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=877&w=612", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/au/batch_au_gaston_ver01/data/sn85038485/00340583954/1910073101/0448.xml&format=alto_xml"], "index": 3, "language": ["english"], "location": ["alabama", "birmingham", "united states", "jefferson"], "location_city": ["birmingham"], "location_country": ["united states